{"tid":2057174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七一衝擊立法會  劉頴匡孫曉嵐等多人改控暴動明日【東區裁判法院】提堂","createTime":"2020-06-09T07:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T11:25:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"791e3233c223a044bf35cbd80916c31325d15815","tid":2057174,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YycVz.kN.mu2Ah8xfr.i9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/C-71-200609-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYycVz.kN.mu2Ah8xfr.i9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FC-71-200609-13.jpg&h=c1e11bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】七一衝擊立法會案，港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐等人進入或逗留在會議廳範圍，被改控暴動罪，案件周三提堂。<br />\n<br />\n七一衝擊立法會案十多名被告，包括前港大學生會會長孫曉嵐及藝人王宗堯等，原本被控一項進入或逗留在會議廳範圍，控方在上一次法庭把四宗案件合併。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名被告，民間集會團隊發言人劉頴匡指今日代表律師收到通知，十多名被告的控罪同樣會被改為暴動罪，星期三在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/七-衝擊立法會-劉頴匡孫曉嵐等多人改控暴動明日提堂-053938351.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%B8%83-%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E5%8A%89%E9%A0%B4%E5%8C%A1%E5%AD%AB%E6%9B%89%E5%B5%90%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%B9%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82-053938351.html&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=8695a12b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/七-衝擊立法會-劉頴匡孫曉嵐等多人改控暴動明日提堂-053938351.html</a>"},{"pid":"540b743430b0fac3e7edb8bacd162f5fb85a0ebe","tid":2057174,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj